  "texts": [
    "The latter are to estimate and recommend the parameters of the policy models based on the available policy datasets.",
    "In this direction, a web interface for the policy extraction is e10-10 Thanasis Papadakis et al.",
    "provided, which offers two main views, a view for AI experts and a view for policymakers.",
    "The \"AI expert\" view empowers AI experts to select a project and work on it (Figure 7).",
    "Likewise, the policymaker view enables policymakers to test AI models for a specific policy KPI."
  ]
